{"tid":323331,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"重考泊車 澤安道","createTime":"2017-07-15T13:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T15:55:37.000Z","uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8526053d8fa102711f1dff297f72c761d7ad1e","tid":323331,"uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T13:49:34.000Z","msg":"下星期會係澤安道重考泊車（棍波）<br />\n因為平時唔入得考場，係出面練調頭同泊車啲線好亂<br />\n<br />\n想知多少少個考場啲線係點，有冇巴打可以分享下個流程同埋注意地方<br />\n真係唔想再考多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0b6f3e9c1c8eb701c5df677b76fe3c134652d1","tid":323331,"uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:04:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下星期會係澤安道重考泊車（棍波）<br />\n因為平時唔入得考場，係出面練調頭同泊車啲線好亂<br />\n<br />\n想知多少少個考場啲線係點，有冇巴打可以分享下個流程同埋注意地方<br />\n真係唔想再考多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npish"},{"pid":"59ed2cc6a1ea75b46a6459fc0e48038481818e6e","tid":323331,"uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下星期會係澤安道重考泊車（棍波）<br />\n因為平時唔入得考場，係出面練調頭同泊車啲線好亂<br />\n<br />\n想知多少少個考場啲線係點，有冇巴打可以分享下個流程同埋注意地方<br />\n真係唔想再考多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npish</blockquote><br />\npish"},{"pid":"cd5d63125d5d09f8c85356adaefe87ae71344d23","tid":323331,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:12:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下星期會係澤安道重考泊車（棍波）<br />\n因為平時唔入得考場，係出面練調頭同泊車啲線好亂<br />\n<br />\n想知多少少個考場啲線係點，有冇巴打可以分享下個流程同埋注意地方<br />\n真係唔想再考多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問師傅"},{"pid":"dc170045cba12288038cfee39ab4467431e5ba36","tid":323331,"uid":53837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"好正常既線黎    好清楚有幾個位比你  考官會叫你泊其中一個   <br />\n好易"},{"pid":"a8eb3dc0524a6c0e4dc33dc6f76fddb7e3c4f10e","tid":323331,"uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好正常既線黎    好清楚有幾個位比你  考官會叫你泊其中一個   <br />\n好易</blockquote><br />\n咁係調頭先定泊車先"},{"pid":"4dc7fc5ea478545f65b1a8f074b9a0952dd829ad","tid":323331,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好正常既線黎    好清楚有幾個位比你  考官會叫你泊其中一個   <br />\n好易</blockquote><br />\n咁係調頭先定泊車先</blockquote><br />\n泊先"},{"pid":"26a068785a477864252ee641d53e320be8515b49","tid":323331,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:02:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好正常既線黎    好清楚有幾個位比你  考官會叫你泊其中一個   <br />\n好易</blockquote><br />\n咁係調頭先定泊車先</blockquote><br />\n三手調頭先, 之後就泊車,<br />\n平時練開試場出面果個位就OK, 入到去都係咁做"},{"pid":"d3877b8675f2e333ae464e3436156a97cc8af843","tid":323331,"uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好正常既線黎    好清楚有幾個位比你  考官會叫你泊其中一個   <br />\n好易</blockquote><br />\n咁係調頭先定泊車先</blockquote><br />\n三手調頭先, 之後就泊車,<br />\n平時練開試場出面果個位就OK, 入到去都係咁做</blockquote><br />\n我師父就話泊車先<br />\n其實我唔係唔問佢 係佢年紀大<br />\n講野一舊舊 有時我真係理解唔到<br />\n又要渣車 又要聽佢講<br />\n所以先想係度問清楚啲<br />\n<br />\n係唔係即係有機會泊車同調頭個次序唔同<br />\n係場出面線又斜又唔清楚<br />\n師父就屌我回車都回唔直，又話泊完車之後得好少位比你調頭<br />\n搞到我好緊要，又無得入去望下<br />\n我上網搵左張圖，有冇考過嘅巴打可以同我分享下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/230841_5822e324e3bed7d0cbfebaa79bb07d2a.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F230841_5822e324e3bed7d0cbfebaa79bb07d2a.PNG&h=7c19d1a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0fc2adb4e5da39314488990ce0e1279f174ff4d","tid":323331,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:16:15.000Z","msg":"我6月果時考係調頭先, 可能個個考官唔同"},{"pid":"433edf72e74e8b75aff684f4eacf4213935ea576","tid":323331,"uid":4057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:18:11.000Z","msg":"應該可以入考場睇？ 我果時考前一日都入考場睇人考"},{"pid":"9ed30e091ec8aebe5d62c756f79f001347e15705","tid":323331,"uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我6月果時考係調頭先, 可能個個考官唔同</blockquote><br />\n咁你係唔係直入去調頭<br />\n跟住直出就岩岩好泊車？"},{"pid":"ac664b6a0ff7db19fed73a7a30e6af13fee2826a","tid":323331,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我6月果時考係調頭先, 可能個個考官唔同</blockquote><br />\n咁你係唔係直入去調頭<br />\n跟住直出就岩岩好泊車？</blockquote><br />\n係, 直入中間果個黃格調頭, 調完轉出黎就泊得, 泊完就路試"},{"pid":"950dd07c3b6b541411a1391ad17d5900bd1138aa","tid":323331,"uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我6月果時考係調頭先, 可能個個考官唔同</blockquote><br />\n咁你係唔係直入去調頭<br />\n跟住直出就岩岩好泊車？</blockquote><br />\n係, 直入中間果個黃格調頭, 調完轉出黎就泊得, 泊完就路試</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/232917_5822e324e3bed7d0cbfebaa79bb07d2a.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F232917_5822e324e3bed7d0cbfebaa79bb07d2a.PNG&h=3af4a30b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係唔係即係咁？<br />\n<br />\n可能我只係需要考泊車，所以泊完先調頭<br />\n<br />\n樓上位巴打 你泊車先個路線係點"},{"pid":"07ae45295b169b2ed7e1c2c0019e0d8bf3d89954","tid":323331,"uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好正常既線黎    好清楚有幾個位比你  考官會叫你泊其中一個   <br />\n好易</blockquote><br />\n咁係調頭先定泊車先</blockquote><br />\n泊先</blockquote><br />\n巴打 係唔係重考泊車only？<br />\n可唔可分享下流程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c89d6617957d117ddd3d0298dae2144659d69cc","tid":323331,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我6月果時考係調頭先, 可能個個考官唔同</blockquote><br />\n咁你係唔係直入去調頭<br />\n跟住直出就岩岩好泊車？</blockquote><br />\n係, 直入中間果個黃格調頭, 調完轉出黎就泊得, 泊完就路試</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/232917_5822e324e3bed7d0cbfebaa79bb07d2a.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F232917_5822e324e3bed7d0cbfebaa79bb07d2a.PNG&h=3af4a30b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係唔係即係咁？<br />\n<br />\n可能我只係需要考泊車，所以泊完先調頭<br />\n<br />\n樓上位巴打 你泊車先個路線係點</blockquote><br />\nYES"},{"pid":"7bfc37f6479a5e348d39c3aaae83f0883b9a25e2","tid":323331,"uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我6月果時考係調頭先, 可能個個考官唔同</blockquote><br />\n咁你係唔係直入去調頭<br />\n跟住直出就岩岩好泊車？</blockquote><br />\n係, 直入中間果個黃格調頭, 調完轉出黎就泊得, 泊完就路試</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/232917_5822e324e3bed7d0cbfebaa79bb07d2a.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F232917_5822e324e3bed7d0cbfebaa79bb07d2a.PNG&h=3af4a30b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係唔係即係咁？<br />\n<br />\n可能我只係需要考泊車，所以泊完先調頭<br />\n<br />\n樓上位巴打 你泊車先個路線係點</blockquote><br />\nYES</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該哂你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c367e52c03337a39b35b2e96429eb9bd14a48b9","tid":323331,"uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好正常既線黎    好清楚有幾個位比你  考官會叫你泊其中一個   <br />\n好易</blockquote><br />\n咁係調頭先定泊車先</blockquote><br />\n泊先</blockquote><br />\n巴打 係唔係重考泊車only？<br />\n可唔可分享下流程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5af2e6d6268bf73e1419a35769d99b2ce48ec6e","tid":323331,"uid":86354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好正常既線黎    好清楚有幾個位比你  考官會叫你泊其中一個   <br />\n好易</blockquote><br />\n咁係調頭先定泊車先</blockquote><br />\n泊先</blockquote><br />\n巴打 係唔係重考泊車only？<br />\n可唔可分享下流程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npish"}]}